<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> تَفْسِيرُ الآيَتَينِ فِي آلِ عِمْرَانَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> النَّهْيُ الصَّرِيحُ عَنْ قَولٍ: <span class="c2">(لَو)</span> إِذَا أَصَابَكَ شَيءٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> تَعْلِيلُ المَسْأَلَةِ بِأَنَّ ذَلِكَ يَفْتَحُ عَمَلَ الشَّيطَانِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> الإِرْشَادُ إِلَى الكَلَامِ الحَسَنِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> الأَمْرُ بِالحِرْصِ عَلَى مَا يَنْفَعُ مَعَ الِاسْتِعَانَةِ بِاللَّهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسَةُ:</span> النَّهْيُ عَنْ ضِدِّ ذَلِكَ؛ وَهُوَ العَجْزُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>